# =============================================================================
# HOW TO SET UP SENTRY
# =============================================================================

# 1. Create accounts at https://sentry.io/
# 2. Create separate projects for:
#    - Backend (Python/Django)
#    - Frontend (JavaScript/React)
#    - Celery Workers (Python/Celery) - can use same as backend
# 3. Copy the DSN from each project
# 4. Replace the placeholder values above
# 5. Set up alerts and monitoring rules
# 6. Test error reporting in each environment

# Example Sentry Projects Structure:
# JAC Learning Platform/
# ├── Backend API (Python/Django)
# ├── Frontend App (React/TypeScript)
# └── Celery Workers (Python tasks) - optional, use backend DSN

